This strategy is a short-term momentum approach based on moving averages and volume. Studies show it performs more effectively on the 1-hour and 4-hour timeframes. Take-profit and stop-loss distances are kept short, resulting in a high win rate, while the profit factor ranges between 1.4 and 2.
